articles.description:
RT Billyjitsu ⟁
Banger 👇

koeppelmann.eth 🦉💳: @notjuve Because we want to scale Ethereum, and on Ethereum, contracts—wherever they are—need to be able to message each other. So, if you cannot reliably message from one L2 contract to another L2 contract, those L2s are NOT Ethereum.
There is room for liquidity bridges and app-layer
